Scoutmarkt isimli database icin duzenlenmis dosyalar. Yenisini eklerken su formata uyarsaniz sevinirim:

pageName.php
pageNameprocess.php 

pageNameprocess dosyasinin icinde su kisim bulunmali:

$dbhost = "127.0.0.1";
$dbuser = "root";
$dbpass = "";
$db = "scoutmarkt_db";

// Create connection
$conn = new mysqli($dbhost, $dbuser, $dbpass, $db);
// Check connection
if ($conn->connect_error) {
  die("Connection failed: " . $conn->connect_error);
}
